for generate private key ::: `openssl ecparam -name c2tnb431r1 -genkey > yourprivatekey`
then to public ::: `openssl ec -pubout -in yourpublickey -out publickey` and post public key or comment
now compute common secret key ::: `pass=$(openssl pkeyutl -derive -inkey -inkey yourprivatekey -peerkey publickey | base64 -w 0)`
